Package: matxingraphout
Title: Convert Adjacency Matrices to SVG, DOT, and Mermaid Graphs
Version: 0.3.1
Authors@R:
    person("Shimpei", "Morimoto", email = "your@email.com",
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Takes an adjacency matrix and a node-property table and returns
    a rendered SVG file, Graphviz DOT source, and Mermaid flowchart source.
    No external package dependencies.
